                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12551</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the hdfs directory for the region is removed, and HBCK is invoked to fix the issue. The test fails flakily because the region is removed from meta and unassigned, but the region is not offlined from the masters in-memory.&lt;/p&gt;

